=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;"> emphasize in their public statements</a> =E2=
=80=94=C2=A0is that ESG investing is supposed to <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25498985.267682/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJn=
LmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDctMDgvc29tZW9uZS1pcy1nb2luZy10by1kcml=
sbC10aGUtb2lsP2NtcGlkPUJCRDEwMjgyMV9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdX=
