=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> get=C2=A0<em>higher ret=
urns=C2=A0</em>in the long run</a>, because good-ESG businesses are <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25498985.267682/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMTAtMDQvZmFjZWJvb2st=
d2hpc3RsZWJsb3dlci1zaG93cy1hLXNoaWZ0LWluLXNoYXJlaG9sZGVyLXZhbHVlcy1hd2F5LWZ=
yb20tcHJvZml0cz9jbXBpZD1CQkQxMDI4MjFfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJn=
