none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> more sustainable</a> th=
an bad-ESG businesses. If you pollute, you might make a lot of money now, b=
ut <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/25498985.267682=
/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDktMTQvZG=
